{"title":"Merida One-Twenty Alloy Mountain Bike Gets 130mm Travel, a 110mm Ninety-Six Lite, too!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/merida-one-twenty-alloy-mountain-bike-gets-130mm-travel-a-110mm-ninety-six-lite-too/","date":1695970800000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike, Cory riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Merida revamps their core One-Twenty full-suspension mountain bike with a simplified design and a bit more travel to create an even more capable all-rounder trail bike for the masses. With 130mm of travel front and rear, call it a downcountry bike if you want. Or maybe more appropriately – a short travel trail bike, Or more simply, just a mountain bike. And it’s only available in aluminum. That then, makes sure to keep the new One-Twenty affordable and accessible to anyone out hunting trail to ride.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Oh, and if you like the recent carbon Ninety-Six cross country update, but are on a budget? There’s a new Lite alloy setup for that type of marathon riding, too…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Merida One-Twenty an affordable 130mm alloy mountain bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, sunset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_sunset-in-Exmoor-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption><em>photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/corywadebenson\" target=\"_blank\">Cory Benson</a>, c. <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bikerumor\" target=\"_blank\">Bikerumor</a></em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Following in the footsteps of last year’s One-Forty &amp; One-Sixty platform, Merida revamps the One-Twenty. It gets a new simplified suspension design, an alloy-only frame, and modernized geometry.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s get this out of the way quickly… The new Merida One-Twenty is a 130mm travel mountain bike. It originated at 120 in the back, 120 in the front. Then, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/exclusive-all-new-2019-merida-one-twenty-trail-mountain-bike-is-more-capable-than-ever/\" target=\"_blank\">120 rear &amp; 130mm up front</a>. Now, it’s just 130mm front &amp; rear. The bike has been around in essentially 5 generations since it debuted in 2009. And a lot has changed in almost 15 years – from 26″ wheels and 3x drivetrains to this modern 1x-specific 29er. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike, Cory riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_Cory-riding-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/merida.bikes/\" target=\"_blank\">Merida</a>, photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/paulboxphotography\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Box</a></em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But it’s still a mid-travel mountain bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And it’s still meant to be ridden on pretty much any trails you want. Pedal uphill like a short-travel bike, bomb down almost like a long-travel gravity bike. It continues to evolve, yet it’s still just a mountain bike. So, Merida has kept the One-Twenty name. Argue with them, not me.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty 700, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike, detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Merida envisions the One-Twenty as the kind of versatile bike that’s well-suited for everything from a rider’s first entry in discovering singletrack riding to all-day backcountry trail riding for more experienced mountain bikers. So, this new update focuses on a few key points: simplicity, affordability &amp; modern trail capability.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Keep it simple (stupid)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_all-new-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption><em>photos c. Merida</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Keeping this simple means making the bike easy to setup and last a long time.  To that goal, Merida shifted to the same simplified single pivot design as the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2023-merida-160-140-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\">140/160</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-reshaped-2021-merida-ninety-six-race-mountain-bike-stretches-out-for-xc-and-trail/\" target=\"_blank\">96</a>. That uses flex in the P-Flex aluminum seatstays to eliminate the need for a pivot near the axle. And it upgrades to larger main pivot bearings. They also rearranged the short linkage-driven shock layout. It is now reconfigured under the toptube to make more space for two regular water bottles, plus a mount for a spare tube &amp; tools. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, rear end new suspension\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_new-suspension-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new design with the seatstays effectively acting as springs, means a more progressive suspension leverage ratio. That necessitates a custom tune for the air shocks. But it also means greater support at the end of the travel, letting you send it on this relatively short-travel bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All-in, it’s now also Category 4 tested for use up to enduro racing, with a lifetime original owner frame warranty.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, internal cable routing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_cable-routing-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Old school internal cable routing ports also disappear, going for internal cable routing through the oversized 1.5″ Acros headset. The new routing also has foam sleeves for rattle-free riding. And it adds a service port at the BB for easy cable replacement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Make it affordable in aluminum</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing.jpg\"><img width=\"990\" height=\"555\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, Zedler Institut alloy testing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing.jpg 990w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing-800x448.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing-768x431.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Zedler-institute-alloy-testing-400x225.jpg 400w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Maintaining affordability essentially comes down to sticking only with an aluminum frame. The new 5th generation One-Twenty uses a LITE alloy frame made of triple-butted Prolite 66 hydroformed aluminum tubing, with big chunky smooth welds. Five years of commercial inflation means that the top-spec bike is more expensive than the old top alloy bike. But Merida still managed to build up a new entry-level complete trail bike cheaper than they did back in 2019.</p>\n\n\n\nHow much does it weigh, though?\n<p>The new claimed frame weight is 3100g without shock, down just 20g from the previous shorter-travel iteration (<em>or up 80g depending on how they compare it</em>). It’s also more than 500g lighter than the recent alloy One-Forty frame. The top-tier alloy Merida One-Twenty 700 that I tested weighed 15kg, just 100g more than a similarly spec’d <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/exclusive-all-new-2019-merida-one-twenty-trail-mountain-bike-is-more-capable-than-ever/\" target=\"_blank\">One Twenty 800</a> from the previous generation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Shred harder with more travel &amp; modern geometry</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"975\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, new geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-297x145.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-800x390.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-120x59.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-768x374.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-1536x749.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As for extra capability, the bump up to 130mm of rear wheel travel certainly helps to some degree. An extra 10mm of travel can do wonders for making a bike’s ride plush, while still having something in reserve for bigger bumps. But it’s really the more modern longer, lower, slacker enduro-inspired geometry that makes the biggest difference. Now with a slacker 66° headtube, a steep 78.5° seattube, the same 435mm chainstays, and 1-3cm longer Reach – the bike climbs &amp; descends faster. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"550\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, geo comparison\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons-297x91.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons-800x244.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons-120x37.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons-768x235.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_geometry-comparisons-1536x469.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It also puts it right smack dab in between the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-reshaped-2021-merida-ninety-six-race-mountain-bike-stretches-out-for-xc-and-trail/\" target=\"_blank\">Ninety-Six</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2023-merida-160-140-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\">One-Forty</a> on Stack, Reach, and angles.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, agilometer sizing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing-297x124.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing-800x333.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing-120x50.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_Agilometer-sizing-768x320.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, like the 140/160, the new 120 shifts to Merida Agilometer sizing that adds a 5th framesize, and relabels them. From XShort to Mid to XLong, standover heights are generally reduced with longer travel droppers. That then, lets most riders pick from 2 or 3 different frame sizes. Get the Reach that they prefer, without worrying over conventional sizing. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go shorter for a more playful ride, or longer for extra stability at speed.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, angled rear end\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-end-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Beyond the new aluminum frame design and its performance improvements, Merida also sticks with solid proven standards. The new One-Twenty features a Boost thru-axles with a SRAM UDH for future-proof derailleur or ‘transmission’ drivetrain setups. It also keeps a threaded BSA bottom bracket, with an optional set of bolt-on ISCG05 tabs if you feel the need for a chainguide. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It features long 34.9mm dropper posts for reliability (150mm for XS &amp; S, 170mm for M, and 200mm for L &amp; XL). And it gets ribbed chainstay &amp; inner seatstay protectors, plus a long downtube protector to keep the bike quiet and looking good.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, water bottle mounts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_water-bottle-mounts-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike has room for 2 water bottles across all sizes – 0.5L on the seattube &amp; 0.5-0.75L on the downtube depending on size. Plus, there’s another 2-bolt mount under the toptube to mount another accessory like a strap mount or tool bag. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike details, rear brake cooling fins\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_rear-brake-cooling-fins-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It also builds brake cooling fins into the post mount rear disc tabs that separate braking from seatstay flex. There’s also an optional long bolt-on rear fender (shared with the 160) to keep muck away from your pivots if you ride a lot on muddy trails.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2024 Merida One-Twenty – Pricing, Options &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty 700, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-700_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Merida One-Twenty 700</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 2024 Merida One-Twenty comes in three specs, each with a colorful frame option or the gray version like my test bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The top spec is a £3100 / 3720€ One-Twenty 700 with a mechanical SRAM NX Eagle drivetrain, DB8 4-piston brakes, RockShox Pike Select/Deluxe Select+ suspension, and house brand 29mm internal alloy wheels with 2.4″ Maxxis Forekaster tires (tubeless-ready, but without tubeless tape, valves, or sealant.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty 600, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-600_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Merida One-Twenty 600</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then a £2500 / 3000€ One-Twenty 600 opts for a Deore 1×12 group, Deore 4/2-piston brake combo, a Marzocchi Z2 fork paired to the same RockShox Deluxe Select+ shock, and the same wheel/tire combo.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty 300, affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-300_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Merida One-Twenty 300</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And lastly, an entry-level One-Twenty 300 is Merida’s most affordable trail bike in years at £1900 / 2280€, with a Shimano Cues LinkGlide 1×10 drivetrain, Shimano 2-piston brakes, SR Suntour 2CR XCR34 fork &amp; Edge Plus shock, and 25mm internal tubeless-ready wheels with 2.4″ Rekon wire bead tires.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All of the new One-Twenties are making their way around the globe now on their way to Merida dealer bike shops. They should be available everywhere in October.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro.jpg\" alt=\"Merida One-Twenty_affordable 130mm aluminum alloy Lite trail mountain bike, riding The EX enduro race\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty_affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-Lite-trail-mountain-bike_photo-by-Paul-Box_carving-the-rainy-EX-enduro-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. Merida, photo by Paul Box</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But, how does the new bike ride? Check out our First Rides Review <em>soon</em> from thrashing the new One-Twenty through The Ex Enduro to see how it fared. And how beat up I was after 5 intense days of technical UK riding!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>But what about the alloy Merida Ninety-Six Lite?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida Ninety-Six Lite, affordable 115mm aluminum alloy cross-country marathon mountain bike, frameset detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_frameset-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Eagle-eyed mountain bikers may notice that this 130mm alloy trail bike’s design looks a lot like the 100mm travel <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-reshaped-2021-merida-ninety-six-race-mountain-bike-stretches-out-for-xc-and-trail/\" target=\"_blank\">Ninety-Six XC bike</a> from a couple of years ago. And that Ninety-Six is still only available in a carbon frame option – either in XC or light trail builds.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So to make a Ninety-Six on a budget, Merida realized they could scale down the new aluminum One-Twenty by simply giving it a shorter travel fork and a shorter stroke shock. It’s the same triple-butted alloy Lite frame as for the One-Twenty. Only now it’s reduced travel to 110mm front &amp; rear, which puts it in between the racy RC and downcountry trail builds of the carbon cross-country bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"975\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida Ninety-Six Lite, affordable 115mm aluminum alloy cross-country marathon mountain bike, geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry-297x145.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry-800x390.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry-120x59.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry-768x374.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-Lite_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike_geometry-1536x749.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Geometry-wise you get a one degree steeper setup with 67° head angle, ultra steep 79.5° seat angle (maybe slide the saddle back a bit on the rails), and the same 435mm rear end. Leaning the bike forward a bit does lower the BB by 7mm, and extend frame Reach by 10mm &amp; lower Stack by 8mm across all sizes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Build-wise, the Ninety-Six Lite gets a lighter setup. That means a lighter 34mm stanchion forks and 31.8 cockpit for the 96 vs. the 35 &amp; 35 on 120. It also means faster-rolling Rekon Race tires vs. the Forekasters, and 2-piston brakes on all models. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The end goal of the new Ninety-Six Lite is an affordable marathon cross-country bike. Compare that vs. the trail focus of the One-Twenty Lite.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2024 Merida Ninety-Six Lite – Pricing, Options &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida Ninety-Six XT-Edition, affordable 115mm aluminum alloy cross-country marathon mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-XT-Edition_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Merida Ninety-Six Lite XT-Edition</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Two alloy Merida Ninety-Six Lite models enter the 2024 lineup, each in color or black. The top-tier is the still reasonable £2900 / 3500€ Ninety-Six XT-edition, with you guessed it… a Shimano XT 1×12 build with RockShox SID SL/Deluxe Select+ suspension and 25mm internal alloy wheels. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida Ninety-Six Lite 400, affordable 115mm aluminum alloy cross-country marathon mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-Ninety-Six-400_affordable-115mm-aluminum-alloy-cross-country-marathon-mountain-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Merida Ninety-Six Lite 400</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Or pick the even more affordable Ninety-Six 400 for just £2100 / 2500€. That gets a Deore 1×12 build and SR Suntour Raidon 34 R/Edge Plus suspension. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Merida One-Twenty Lite affordable 130mm aluminum alloy trail mountain bike, riding\n\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2024-Merida-One-Twenty-Lite-affordable-130mm-aluminum-alloy-trail-mountain-bike_trail-riding-close-up-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. Merida</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Just like the recent <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/merida-one-sixty-fr-alloy-bikepark-enduro-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">One-Sixty FR</a>, all of the new 2024 Ninety-Six Lites and One-Twenties will be arriving within weeks at Merida dealers around the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://merida-bikes.com\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Merida-bikes.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/merida-one-twenty-alloy-mountain-bike-gets-130mm-travel-a-110mm-ninety-six-lite-too/\">Merida One-Twenty Alloy Mountain Bike Gets 130mm Travel, a 110mm Ninety-Six Lite, too!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"5b18eef553587abd9092334b97e59274d138b77931da6fc6d03fea8b31883870","category":"Cycling"}